{
  "stem": "1581.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "With-- we didn't have any communists in Austria, but the Social Democrats were the-- the leftists.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there were definitely signs that this was a rising power.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They also had-- when later on, the Nazi party was outlawed, they found another method.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They wore white stockings.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And you know, they had-- whoever wore a white stocking was a Nazi.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it-- it was frightening how many there were.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, when I graduated, I-- I did what you would call here a rotating internship.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I got my postgraduate education in various Viennese hospitals.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was for the next two years until I was called in for the army.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was always a latent creeping anti-Semitism, although it was not in the open until Hitler came to power.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But it did not really interfere with my education.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We-- we could go after our business.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, on October 1st of 1936, I entered the Czech army and served for two years.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Being a doctor, we had a special basic training in Prague.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was a very rough basic training.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I can easily say now that this probably is also one of the items that made me survive during the bad years to come, because we were really in-- in good-- good shape.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "After the basic training, I was a physician in the Czech army.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was a officer.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I had, to be honest, a wonderful time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was no-- there was hardly any anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If I say hardly, among us doctors, there were a lot who didn't make any secret of it that they are anti-Semites.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nevertheless, they-- they did not talk to me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had no social contact with me.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
